name: Sausage Strike
description:
Content Description:
After a fierce war, you are the only survivor.
In this inhumane world, survival is the primary goal. This is your own kingdom.
No one will pity you. Let's make our own world with our own hands and guard the place where we live.
As long as we resist the attack of evil forces, we can win the final victory.
What are you waiting for? Come and accept the test of evil power!!

Game Features:
1.This is a war between two castles.
2.This is a tower defense game.
3.The character's weapon has unlimited bullets.
